config.user_prompt_template:
Customer query: {query}

Classify this query into one of: 'billing', 'shipping', 'returns', 'other'.

Return JSON:
{{
  "category": "<category>",
  "confidence": <0-1>,
  "reasoning": "<brief explanation>"
}}

Customer ID: {customer_id}
Billing Issue: {query}

Resolve the billing issue following company policy. Return JSON:
{{
  "issue_type": "<type>",
  "resolution": "<action taken>",
  "status": "resolved" or "escalated",
  "confidence": <0-1>
}}

Customer ID: {customer_id}
Shipping Issue: {query}

Resolve the shipping issue. Return JSON:
{{
  "issue_type": "<type>",
  "resolution": "<action taken>",
  "status": "resolved" or "escalated",
  "tracking_update": "<if applicable>",
  "confidence": <0-1>
}}

Customer ID: {customer_id}
Return Request: {query}

Process the return request following return policy. Return JSON:
{{
  "issue_type": "<type>",
  "eligibility": "eligible" or "ineligible",
  "resolution": "<action taken>",
  "status": "resolved" or "escalated",
  "confidence": <0-1>
}}

Unresolved Issue:
Query: {query}
Customer ID: {customer_id}
Attempted Resolution: {attempts}

Create escalation ticket summary. Return JSON:
{{
  "ticket_id": "<generated>",
  "summary": "<issue summary>",
  "priority": "high" or "normal",
  "context": "<customer context for agent>",
  "next_steps": "<recommended actions>"
}}
